data.description: Large, move in ready historic home in the city of Rockmart featuring 5 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Gorgeous, deep, wraparound front porch, master on main, private owner's bath with a claw foot tub, and 4 large bedrooms upstairs. Hardwood and tile floors, large kitchen, and separate dining room. Main floor laundry room, plus an additional flex space perfect for a home office or studio. The home features 6 decorative fireplaces, 10 ft. high ceilings on the main and upstairs, and historical decorative trim and fixtures throughout. This home is perfect for someone wanting the nostalgia and elegance of the past, with a short sidewalk walk to historic downtown, great restaurants, and the Silver Comet Trail. The house sits on a large corner lot with a private fenced backyard and a covered rear porch. There's also an outbuilding perfect for storage or a future flex space/in-law suite. Newer roof, water heater and HVAC. No HOA.
